      "description": "I work with conceptual art in different techniques and materials; it´s the idea which decides how the presentation will be. I find it most interesting working with installations placed on unexpected public areas. Whatever technique characterises my work of time consuming precision and consists of several dimensions with strong feeling for colour, form and material. I have for many years been investigating the theme of 'LIFE'.",
